\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
Let 
\begin_inset Formula $f:\mathbb{R}\to\left(0,1\right)$
\end_inset

 be defined as 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f\left(x\right)=\frac{\arctan\left(x\right)+\frac{\pi}{2}}{\pi},
